        "note_tweet": {
          "entities": {},
          "text": "A little fun behind-the-scenes story about our Nicole video!\n\nLohen was too focused on fighting to open the chest, but inside his chest was actually his new weapon, “Disaster and Remorse”.\nSo maybe that’s why Nicole looked even more disappointed lol.\n\nWe chose the Cryo Abyss Mage as Lohen’s opponent because we wanted to show his personality — the type who would fight head-on without caring about shield elements.\nBut since in-game details are still important, we also added the Scarlet Quartz effect, which can break Cryo shields!\n\nAnd finally, I’m not sure if anyone noticed, but the BGM used in this video was from the PV where Klee’s witch outfit first appeared.\nWe wanted to choose music that felt cute while also being connected to the Hexenzirkel, so we also had Klee wear her adorable witch outfit to match the BGM!\n\nPlease give this video lots of love too~ Thank you so much, everyone! 😎"
        },
